8
00:00:21,488 --> 00:00:23,004
TO THE WEDNESDAY AFTERNOON
FLIGHT.

9
00:00:23,040 --> 00:00:25,415
FIVE DAYS IN THE BAHAMAS.
(siren wailing in distance)

10
00:00:25,451 --> 00:00:27,834
YOU IN?

11
00:00:27,869 --> 00:00:29,294
EXCELLENT. ALL RIGHT.
I'LL SEE YOU TONIGHT.

12
00:00:29,329 --> 00:00:33,623
(resumes speaking Mandarin)

13
00:00:33,659 --> 00:00:36,125
