15
00:00:38,255 --> 00:00:41,490
(speaking German)

16
00:00:53,654 --> 00:00:55,153
(man) THERE'S NO WAY
THEY'RE GONNA GIVE HER

17
00:00:55,188 --> 00:00:56,921
THE INTERNATIONAL POSITION.

18
00:00:56,957 --> 00:00:59,816
BECAUSE SOONER OR LATER,

19
00:00:59,852 --> 00:01:02,093
SHE'S GONNA DRINK
THE MARRIAGE AND BABY PUNCH,

