THEY'RE IN THE BOARDROOM NOW,
AND YOU HAVE TWO MINUTES.

28
00:01:22,307 --> 00:01:25,375
OH, AND YOUR MOM CALLED...
AGAIN.

29
00:01:25,377 --> 00:01:27,419
WONDERING IF YOU'RE COMING HOME
FOR THANKSGIVING.

30
00:01:27,454 --> 00:01:30,263
