IN A PLASTIC BAG

808
00:37:56,616 --> 00:37:58,950
SO I DIDN'T LOSE YOUR SMELL.

809
00:37:58,986 --> 00:38:01,051
OKAY, THAT'S A LITTLE
STALKER-Y, BUT GO AHEAD.

810
00:38:01,087 --> 00:38:03,138
