WHY DIDN'T YOU COME
AFTER ME?

821
00:38:23,368 --> 00:38:25,126
WHAT?

822
00:38:26,505 --> 00:38:29,021
YOU TOLD ME.

823
00:38:29,057 --> 00:38:31,941
NO, I WAITED... AND WAITED,
AND YOU NEVER CAME.

824
00:38:31,977 --> 00:38:33,935
AND EVENTUALLY,
THE FEELINGS

825
00:38:33,970 --> 00:38:37,696
OF--OF SUCCESS FILLED UP
THE FEELINGS OF LONELINESS,

826
00:38:37,732 --> 00:38:38,982
AND THEN ALL THE MEN--
THEY COVERED UP

827
00:38:39,017 --> 00:38:42,844
MEMORIES OF YOU, AND THEN,
THE--THE--THE--THE HIGHS

828
00:38:42,879 --> 00:38:45,013
OF MY CAREER LEVELED OUT
THE LOWS

829
