00:48:40,668 --> 00:48:43,836
DID YOU GET YOUR SCONE YET?
NO? OKAY, HANG ON.

1041
00:48:43,838 --> 00:48:45,504
OH, YOU ARE GONNA LOVE THAT.
UH, LET ME GRIND THAT

