1046
00:48:54,532 --> 00:48:55,556
SO TELL PATTY TO CALL ME.

1047
00:48:55,591 --> 00:48:57,099
OKAY, WILL DO.
OKAY.

1048
00:48:57,134 --> 00:49:01,145
(woman) ♪ MAYBE YOU'LL WISH
FOR SOMETHING BETTER ♪

1049
00:49:01,147 --> 00:49:04,348
ALL RIGHT,
SO I GOT TABLE SEVEN.
PERFECT, YEP.

1050
00:49:04,383 --> 00:49:14,158
♪♪

1051
00:49:14,160 --> 00:49:16,535
YEAH, I JUST ARRIVED.
