ITS BUSINESS PERMITS.

1084
00:50:27,967 --> 00:50:30,050
IMAGINE THAT.

1085
00:50:30,086 --> 00:50:32,052
OH, THEY'RE ALL IN CAHOOTS.
THOSE DIRTY RATS.

1086
00:50:32,088 --> 00:50:34,722
WELL, THEY ARE OFFERING
DOUBLE MARKET VALUE

1087
00:50:34,757 --> 00:50:37,116
IN HOPES THAT WE'LL WALK.

